{
    "story_id": "",
    "story_icon": "",
    "outline": {
        "title": "",
        "content": [
            "要跳过此剧情吗？"
        ]
    },
    "story_content": [
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100002_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "埃尔菲莉丝",
            "context": "近来帝国的活动\\n越来越猖獗……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110328_01_04_0001",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100002_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "埃尔菲莉丝",
            "context": "其中最棘手的就是黑暗火炬……\\n放任他们不管的话，这一带的村庄、\\n城镇都会被他们烧成灰烬。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110328_01_04_0002",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "但他们擅长操纵火之魔力，\\n正面交手的话太危险了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110328_01_04_0003",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110328_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "菲约尔姆",
            "context": "那个……各位，\\n能交给我处理吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110328_01_04_0004",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "交给你……\\n你有什么好主意？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110328_01_04_0005",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110328_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "菲约尔姆",
            "context": "嗯。由我当诱饵，\\n把黑暗火焰引过来。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110328_01_04_0006",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "菲约尔姆公主……那可不行。\\n牺牲自己去引诱敌人\\n实在太危险了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110328_01_04_0007",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110328_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "菲约尔姆",
            "context": "能听听\\n我的主意吗……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110328_01_04_0008",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120008_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "帝国兵",
            "context": "即将到达下一目标。\\n让他们见识下我们的力量吧！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110328_01_04_0009",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120081_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "队长",
            "context": "哼哼哼……当然了。\\n胆敢阻挡我们黑暗火炬的家伙，\\n统统化为灰烬！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110328_01_04_0010",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110328_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "菲约尔姆",
            "context": "休想得逞！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110328_01_04_0011",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110328_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "菲约尔姆",
            "context": "残暴的炎之大军，\\n让我来消灭你们！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110328_01_04_0012",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120081_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "队长",
            "context": "竟敢孤身挑战\\n我们黑暗火炬？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110328_01_04_0013",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120081_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "队长",
            "context": "胆子可真不小。\\n好吧，就把你烧成灰，\\n作为下次战斗时用的篝火！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110328_01_04_0014",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110328_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "菲约尔姆",
            "context": "就算只有我一个人，\\n也要和你们战斗到底！\\n呀啊啊啊啊！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110328_01_04_0015",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120081_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "队长",
            "context": "竟然就那样莽撞地冲过来！\\n准备迎战！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110328_01_04_0016",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110328_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "菲约尔姆",
            "context": "呜……我……还不能倒下……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110328_01_04_0017",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120081_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "队长",
            "context": "哼哼哼……也不过是个\\n感情用事的无能之辈。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110328_01_04_0018",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120081_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "队长",
            "context": "别让她跑了！给我追！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110328_01_04_0019",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120008_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "帝国兵",
            "context": "是！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110328_01_04_0020",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110328_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "菲约尔姆",
            "context": "哈啊……哈啊……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110328_01_04_0021",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120081_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "队长",
            "context": "原来如此。以为把我们引到水边\\n就能抑制火焰的威力吗。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110328_01_04_0022",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120081_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "队长",
            "context": "但是很遗憾，\\n光凭这点水，别说抑制火焰了，\\n连牵制住我们都做不到。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110328_01_04_0023",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110328_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "菲约尔姆",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110328_01_04_0024",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120081_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "队长",
            "context": "怎么，已经束手无策了？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110328_01_04_0025",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110328_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "菲约尔姆",
            "context": "不……还有办法。\\n就在你们脚下。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110328_01_04_0026",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120081_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "队长",
            "context": "脚下？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110328_01_04_0027",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120080_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "帝国兵们",
            "context": "哇、哇啊啊啊啊！要、要陷下去了！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110328_01_04_0028",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120081_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "队长",
            "context": "怎么可能！为什么只有我们！？\\n为什么你不会陷下去？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110328_01_04_0029",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110328_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "菲约尔姆",
            "context": "为了拖住敌人，\\n先将其引至湿地吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110328_01_04_0030",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "湿地？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110328_01_04_0031",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110328_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "菲约尔姆",
            "context": "对，送给我药草的孩子\\n曾告诉我。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110328_01_04_0032",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110328_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "菲约尔姆",
            "context": "他说药草丛生的湿地，\\n有很多看不出深浅的地方。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110328_01_04_0033",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "原来如此……乍一看安全，\\n但一旦陷进去就出不来。\\n简直是天然陷阱啊。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110328_01_04_0034",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110328_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "菲约尔姆",
            "context": "是的。\\n村里的大人们\\n都知道那里的地形。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110328_01_04_0035",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100002_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "埃尔菲莉丝",
            "context": "原来如此。\\n只要让他们告诉我们地形，\\n就能安全地移动了呢。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110328_01_04_0036",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110328_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "菲约尔姆",
            "context": "我已经败给黑暗火炬一次，\\n所以他们一定会大意。\\n我们就利用这一点……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110328_01_04_0037",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110328_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "菲约尔姆",
            "context": "尤蒂尔王子，就是现在！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110328_01_04_0038",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "好。\\n各位，我们上！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110328_01_04_0039",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "烧毁了那么多村子和森林……\\n不可原谅！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110328_01_04_0040",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120081_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "队长",
            "context": "可恶……你们快给我反击！\\n把他们统统烧成灰烬！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110328_01_04_0041",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120008_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "帝国兵",
            "context": "不行啊！\\n腿陷在泥里动弹不得！\\n武器也不知去向……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110328_01_04_0042",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120008_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "帝国兵",
            "context": "呃啊啊啊！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110328_01_04_0043",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120081_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "队长",
            "context": "一群没用的废物！\\n该死啊啊啊啊啊啊啊！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110328_01_04_0044",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "打倒了队长，\\n小兵们也四散逃走。\\n这下黑暗火炬也算完了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110328_01_04_0045",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "不过话说回来，\\n菲约尔姆制定的作战计划\\n真是无懈可击啊。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110328_01_04_0046",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100007_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "纳姆",
            "context": "太好了呢，菲约尔姆。\\n这下逃难的人们\\n也终于可以回自己家了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110328_01_04_0047",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110328_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "菲约尔姆",
            "context": "多亏了大家\\n愿意相信我、协助我，\\n非常感谢你们。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110328_01_04_0048",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100002_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "埃尔菲莉丝",
            "context": "我们才要向你道谢，\\n今天能取胜都是你的功劳。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110328_01_04_0049",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110328_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "菲约尔姆",
            "context": "哪里……不过我很高兴能帮上各位的忙。\\n就算将来我回到了原来的世界，\\n也绝对不会忘记今日之战。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110328_01_04_0050",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "是啊……就算离别的那一天来临，\\n我们也绝不会忘记。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110328_01_04_0051",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "不会忘记那位\\n名叫菲约尔姆公主的可靠伙伴……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110328_01_04_0052",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110328_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "菲约尔姆",
            "context": "谢谢你。能与大家……\\n还有尤蒂尔王子相遇，\\n真是太好了！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110328_01_04_0053",
            "book_image": ""
        }
    ]
}